{"tid":834501,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【#Cult片】《暫時停止造愛》(1987)","createTime":"2018-09-24T08:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T05:31:29.000Z","uid":212112,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a667eb9d6a3fd1df90b83fec7c2799a2dbd326cb","tid":834501,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/163901_1b4db3b502eb40b00572739a3c44e5a8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F163901_1b4db3b502eb40b00572739a3c44e5a8.png&h=5f91c632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇情講述一群龍友相約帶三位模特兒，到溪邊進行人體拍攝，模特兒小詩突然人有三急所以在一古墓前解決，並撿到一枚古錢，原來這古錢是一位殭屍所有，小詩的尿而覺醒了，更在小詩被性侵時救了她，後來小詩和另外二位女友為了求得&lsquo;大家樂&rsquo;的明牌找上殭屍(明牌係指彩券開獎前，媒體或「消息靈通人士」甚至通靈人士預測的中獎號碼。)而他告訴她們，可以帶她們&lsquo;大家爽&rsquo;......<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/163903_76e0758aafd1bfdeaa489c7106559ec2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F163903_76e0758aafd1bfdeaa489c7106559ec2.png&h=2e67f508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本影片劇情、配樂、拍攝其實都沒什麼值得落墨，當年經典港產片《殭屍先生》台灣譯名叫《暫時停止呼吸》在當地叫好叫座後的跟風三級片，各種劇情超展開與爆笑下流對白，背後二次創作精神卻是相當浪漫。<br />\n本片香港上映時譯做《殭屍也咸濕》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/163905_e29ef0f66ba165d5a3e8e29c308 23f10.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F163905_e29ef0f66ba165d5a3e8e29c308%2023f10.png&h=dcf613c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/163906_6e07457fb21844daceb2ee7227b38c64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F163906_6e07457fb21844daceb2ee7227b38c64.png&h=3b0ac439&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/163908_3410319ae6d7de4df0e51df53c692190.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F163908_3410319ae6d7de4df0e51df53c692190.png&h=91c95c79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/163910_94fc3f191001e6df0708680a27d9c2a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F163910_94fc3f191001e6df0708680a27d9c2a1.png&h=3a3413f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/163911_a58e062f286260b0dab12d5e0f7dc240.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F163911_a58e062f286260b0dab12d5e0f7dc240.png&h=36b65777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/p/BoGjiKoB7M6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBoGjiKoB7M6%2F&d=P2587STTbFVOIZE5qkrbbgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=afe01fd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fp%2FBoGjiKoB7M6%2F&h=a50f4af3\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/p/BoGjiKoB7M6/</a>"},{"pid":"163c845301f5a35b199468125266947645980c60","tid":834501,"uid":171058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/833869/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/833869/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n同你自己講既野好矛盾<br />\n呢套點Cult法?<br />\n點睇都中哂你講既B級片特徵...."},{"pid":"c950f2d930d0e41ff593c179ce45f2afe34054a6","tid":834501,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"163c845301f5a35b199468125266947645980c60","tid":834501,"uid":171058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/833869/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/833869/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n同你自己講既野好矛盾<br />\n呢套點Cult法?<br />\n點睇都中哂你講既B級片特徵...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T09:14:50.000Z","msg":"哩齣當年喺台灣上映冇人理，跟住喺香港日活院線當咸片再上，都冇人理<br />\n<br />\n但到近年台灣有人考古搵返出嚟公映，吸引左一批台灣cult迷追捧😂"},{"pid":"8e4852485ffa017d77df6984ed2b2c2fb6bf3e1a","tid":834501,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T11:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466aa4adadc0efd4cb537fe88b50f299fb48d976","tid":834501,"uid":212112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}